      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REGGAE MISS (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Healesville following on from a second place finish (24.23) at this track the start prior. Has a good record here at this journey. Looks the one to beat on her best form. COSMIC REWARD (4) turned in a moderate effort last time when seventh at this track over 425m behind Heart (24.76) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Should be about the money. CORNHILL HUSTLER (1) finds it hard to break through. Finished third (24.79) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Expected to be in this for a long way. PAW JANELLE (8) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
